Inventory
    Create a BACKPACK and INVENTORY(?) Class

Actions
    Attack
        Fight in turn, first hit depends on a luck roll
        HP deducted is Luck and Strength
        When mob dies it drops loot

    Flee
        Results in loss of 2 HP and 1 Luck

    Search
        May find a loot item or attract a Mob
              
    Equip / Unequip
        Wear or hold an item

    Use
        Use item


Loot Items
    Create a list of loot items and what they do
    Stats may vary slightly so make them a Class

Mobs
    Create a Mob > Sub-mob class
    Kill count for the player